This is the OPUS command line tool, often used in cron tasks.

Usage:

<scriptname> <function>

this help page only lists prompts that are expected to be useful to OPUS
developers. They usually require a unix like environment in terms of tools
like grep. Use help for more normal parameters.

  check_missing_lang_prompts    check for missing language prompts
  check_missing_error_prompts   check for missing error prompts
  
  help              show command line options for general administration
  

